high_descs: Take a step forward, turn left, go forward and face right side of the oven.
Take the pot from the right side of the stove top.
Turn right, go forward a step, turn right, go forward, turn left at the fridge, go forward to the fridge.
Chill the pot on the top shelf of the fridge. Take the pot from the fridge.
Turn left, go forward, turn left at the square white table, go to the table.
Put the pot on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pot on a table.

high_descs: Turn left and go forward to the stove.
Pick up the pot on the right side of the stove.
Turn around and go straight, then turn left to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the pot inside and chill it, then take the pot out.
Turn around and go to the white table.
Put the pot on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pot on the white table.

high_descs: Turn left and go around the table. Turn slight left again and go forward to the oven.
Pick up the frying pan from the oven.
Turn around to the right and go forward. Turn left and face the fridge.
Place the frying pan in the fridge and then take it out.
Turn to the left then turn left again to turn completely around and walk forward to the table.
Place the frying pan on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a frying pan in the fridge and take it out.
